{"tid":1826570,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「行動post」如果鴨免set死每個台都有限額上熱門，咁其實點拉都無用。","createTime":"2020-01-16T08:47:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T23:15:37.000Z","uid":33359,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"81ac27c8ecfe578c53ee281c3afc51e08daed3ad","tid":1826570,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T08:47:27.000Z","msg":"「&bull; 系統會限制各分台於同一頁中的出現數量，以免內容過於單一。」<br />\n<br />\n例如熱門可以放20個post<br />\nCc台有10個位可以上<br />\n動物台有2個位<br />\n愚樂台又有2個位<br />\nEtc<br />\n<br />\n咁其實你日日屌點解咁既垃圾post都上到熱門都係無用<br />\n因為鴨免分咗限額俾其他台用<br />\n<br />\n兩個解決辦法<br />\n一係就禁止其他台開post<br />\n一係就將cc台post開落其他台到再推上熱門<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bda61615be3623cfe3ae58f781178b057bb7421","tid":1826570,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T08:47:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">歐美議員講野又無人理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n響task2呀 幫手啦上唔到千呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GM2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=d2c21c73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"ac9ae1b2817925d199ea5e75126d12bc95c27f23","tid":1826570,"uid":197393,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T08:52:24.000Z","msg":"係，但好多人都唔知每個台都有限額<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c607685509986b00016bf255fd6aec7679b9bf","tid":182